reviewText: You must have very shaky faith indeed if a admitted work of fiction shakes it so.

I was disappointed in both documentaries.  In fact I consider them less to be documentaries and more subjective conspiracy theories with little objectivity.  With little / no tie into the movie or book, the information is scrambled.  I much prefer the History Channel's dvd on the DaVinci code to this one.
I received the product in a timely manner and in good condition.  Thank you.  I might add, at a great price too!!
